# unisupply release maintainers — public keys allowed to sign vX.Y.Z tags.
#
# Format: <principal> <key-type> <base64-key> [comment]
#   principal : the signer's email, must match git user.email AND the GitHub
#               account's registered Signing Key email.
#   key-type  : ssh-ed25519 (preferred) or ssh-rsa
#   base64-key: the public key body (from ~/.ssh/id_ed25519.pub, field 2)
#
# To add a maintainer: append a line with their email and public key,
# then open a PR against master (will be gated by ci.yml like any other change).
# To remove a maintainer: delete their line and open a PR.
#
# IMPORTANT: Replace the placeholder line below with a real public key before
# the first release. The release workflow will fail on any tag push until at
# least one valid entry exists.
maintainer1@unidoc.io ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzREPLACEWITHREALPUBLICKEY unisupply-release-key-1
# maintainer2@unidoc.io ssh-ed25519 AAAAC3NzREPLACEWITHREALPUBLICKEY unisupply-release-key-2
